trans-unit.source: Represents the resolution supported by a printer.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje rozpoznawania obsługiwane przez drukarkę.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties to get the printer resolutions that are available on the printer and to set the printing resolution for a page, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Ta klasa jest używana przez <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>i <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Właściwości uzyskanie rozdzielczości drukarki, które są dostępne na drukarce i ustawić rozdzielczość drukowania strony, odpowiednio.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> property to determine whether the printer resolution type is the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> value <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: Użyj <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>Właściwości w celu określenia, czy typ rozwiązywania konfliktów drukarki jest <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>wartość <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>

trans-unit.source: If so, use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> properties to determine the printer resolution in the horizontal and vertical directions, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli tak, użyj <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>i <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A>Właściwości, aby określić rozdzielczość drukarki w poziomie i w pionie kierunkach odpowiednio.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information on printing, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: Aby uzyskać więcej informacji na drukowanie, zobacz <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>Omówienie przestrzeni nazw.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.target: Pobiera rozdzielczość pozioma drukarki w punktach na cal.

trans-unit.source: `dmPrintQuality` is a member of the `DEVMODE` (device mode) structure, which defines constants that map to printer quality settings.
trans-unit.target: `dmPrintQuality`jest elementem członkowskim `DEVMODE` struktury (tryb urządzenia), która definiuje stałe, które mapują ustawień jakości drukarki.

trans-unit.source: The X property contains the value `DMRES_HIGH` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, and `DMRES_DRAFT` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: Właściwość X zawiera wartości `DMRES_HIGH` Jeśli <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>ma ustawioną wartość <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` Jeśli <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>ma ustawioną wartość <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` Jeśli <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>ma ustawioną wartość <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, i `DMRES_DRAFT` Jeśli <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>ustawiono <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>
